Interface IColor3R

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ITup3fR, ITup3R, ITupfR, ITupR
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IColor4R, IHDRColor3R, IHDRColor4R, ILDRColor3R, ILDRColor4R
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HDRColor3, HDRColor3Colors, HDRColor4, HDRColor4Colors, LDRColor3, LDRColor3Colors, LDRColor4, LDRColor4Colors, PHDRColor3, PHDRColor4, PLDRColor3, PLDRColor4

    public interface IColor3R
extends ITup3fR
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an RGB-Color.
